| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3598 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 47f270bd-6a92-5c0d-b619-9b6137aaf200"
